# Chapter 1 - Introduction

## Purpose of this chapter@
Chapter 1 introduces the project, its scope and the structure of the further document.

## Constraints and expectations:
  - Assumes farmiliarity with basic linux command-line usage
  - Requires a stable host system that meets specific toolchain requirements
  - Emphasises careful reading and verification at each stage of the build.

This chapter introduces the LFS system, and describes the operating system requirements, which my debian 13 build fits. 

